Use case

Landing page
simple search bar with basic filters

expand to Advance search bar

basic filters:
search by:
trackname
artist
album

sort (Ascending + D):
Alphanumeric 0-Z
Date
Rating (probably breakdown eg x>=3 etc)


Result page:
simple search bar on top

return list of direct or very similar hit
mouse over a element(result?) for a bit more info
click a result to proceed for more detail

